node.text:
Fan favorite and highly requested Chik fil a “Make It Healthy” recipe - if you don’t have a Chik fil a in your state give this recipe a try. You’ll see what the hype is about and find out their secret recipe for making their chicken juicy!- @kickasswithcarly 

1 boneless, skinless chicken breast
1/4 cup pickle juice 
1 egg
1/4 cup milk
1/2 cup almond flour
1 tablespoon powdered sugar
1/2 teaspoon paprika
1/2 teaspoon salt
1/4 teaspoon black pepper
1/4 teaspoon garlic powder
1/4 teaspoon celery salt
